You know what? We may be a team in here,

29:31.780 --> 29:33.490
还有就是
but just so that you know:

29:33.500 --> 29:38.030
当我们逃出去那一刻  我们就要各顾各的了
The minute we get over that wall, it's every man for himself.

29:38.040 --> 29:40.700
或者比那还要早
Or sooner.

29:52.420 --> 29:54.740
LJ?
LJ?

29:57.770 --> 29:59.980
LJ?
LJ?

30:01.020 --> 30:03.120
LJ?
LJ?

30:07.060 --> 30:10.510
