You know how the Russians do things?

30:10.890 --> 30:15.290
他们先让你活着 然后杀掉你全家
They let you live, and they kill everyone else in your family

30:15.300 --> 30:18.510
还有 所有你爱的人
and anyone you've ever loved.

30:18.520 --> 30:19.640
听起来怎么样?
How's that sound?

30:19.650 --> 30:22.220
-去死吧  -噢 来吧
-Go to hell.  -Oh, come on.

30:22.230 --> 30:25.520
