You all right?

31:37.030 --> 31:39.490
斯科菲尔德 别想偷懒
Scofield! No sitting down on the job

31:39.500 --> 31:41.680
过来在我看得到你的地方干活
I want you out here working where I can see you.

31:41.690 --> 31:44.310
马上就来 老大
I'm on it, boss.

31:44.450 --> 31:47.950
快过来 斯科菲尔德  过来!
Move it, Scofield, move it!

32:55.300 --> 32:57.300
