See if we hit it off?

33:39.020 --> 33:42.620
-您贵姓?  -布拉德
-So, what's your name?  -Brad.

33:42.630 --> 33:44.990
-你呢?  -贾斯米
-Yours?  -Jasmine.

33:45.000 --> 33:48.970
