Come on, your real name.

33:49.490 --> 33:53.010
-尼卡  -尼卡
-It's Nika.  -Nika.

33:53.020 --> 33:55.890
这真是个好名字
That's a pretty name.

33:55.900 --> 34:01.870
告诉我 尼卡  你丈夫对你在这工作有什么看法?
Tell me, Nika...How's your husband feel about you working here?

34:01.880 --> 34:03.870
我没结婚
I'm not married.

34:03.880 --> 34:07.070
