I hope you're lying for the sake of titillation.

34:07.080 --> 34:13.080
否则 你今天早上的探监就是违法行为了...
Otherwise, your little visit to Fox River this morning would have been breaking the law.

34:14.170 --> 34:17.690
斯科菲尔德太太
Mrs Scofield.

34:18.650 --> 34:22.050
我们...结婚了 但他们要我们都要撒谎
We are married, but they tell all the girls to lie.

34:22.060 --> 34:23.970
为了生意好做点
It's better for making business.

34:23.980 --> 34:26.650
我不是来找你麻烦的
I'm not here to get you in trouble.

34:26.660 --> 34:30.810
我只是想多了解一下你丈夫
I just want to know a little more about your husband.

34:30.870 --> 34:32.750
嗯 他是个非常好的人
Well, he's a very good man.

34:32.760 --> 34:38.750
我也这么想 但就算是好人也会做坏事
I'm sure he is. But even good men do bad things.

34:39.140 --> 34:44.600
你的口音  是从... 不要告诉我  布达佩斯  是不是?
Your accent. You're from, don't tell me...Budapest, right?

34:44.610 --> 34:47.260
-布拉格  -布拉格...
-Prague.  -Prague.

34:47.270 --> 34:52.270
你来了多久? 两三个月 我猜
How recently did you come over?Only a couple months, I bet.

34:52.280 --> 34:54.000
你喜欢呆在美国?
You like it here in America?

34:54.010 --> 34:55.960
呃  我必须得走了
You know I really I have to move.

34:55.960 --> 34:57.850
他们不想我们在一个顾客呆太久
They don't like us to spend too much time in one spot.

34:57.860 --> 35:02.410
我可不想去查你的移民情况...
Now, I don't want to have to check into your immigration status.

35:02.420 --> 35:04.230
我只想知道
I just need to know

35:04.240 --> 35:09.730
迈克尔·斯科菲尔德让你做什么 来交换你的绿卡
what Michael Scofield wanted from you in exchange for the green card.

35:09.740 --> 35:11.030
什么也没有
Nothing.

35:11.040 --> 35:14.230
他在国外学习时我们认识的...
We met while he was studying overseas.

35:14.240 --> 35:17.230
移民局不会想知道你的那些准备好的故事
I don't want to know what you memorised for the INS.

35:17.240 --> 35:19.990
现在 要么你回答我关于斯科菲尔德的问题
Now, you answer my questions about Scofield,

35:20.000 --> 35:23.150
要不我就打电话 给我芝加哥警局的兄弟了
or I call my guy in the Chicago PD.

35:23.160 --> 35:28.080
或许他会问问有关于你的问题
And maybe he starts asking some questions about you.

35:30.720 --> 35:32.930
一张信用卡
Credit card.

35:32.940 --> 35:37.120
他让我把信用卡给他 就这么多
He asked me to bring him a credit card. That's it.

36:02.680 --> 36:07.240
是的  跟踪这电话  过来找我  马上
Yeah. Trace this call.Come and get me now.

36:07.250 --> 36:09.610
新格莱尔斯 我在新格莱尔斯
New Glarus. I'm in New Glarus.

36:26.050 --> 36:29.410
不用 谢谢 我自己带了
No, thanks. I brought my own.

36:31.930 --> 36:35.920
多尔希·安德鲁·埃尔斯顿·佳比斯
Dorothy Andrews Elston Kabis.

36:35.930 --> 36:39.300
11美国财政部出纳局长 1971
United States treasurer, 1971.

36:39.310 --> 36:43.350
D.B.库珀 劫机那年
The year of the DB Cooper hijacking.

36:44.460 --> 36:48.660
DI192589
Dl192589.

36:48.670 --> 36:54.440
是那笔黑钱的第一张的序列号
The first number in the series of bills used in the ransom drop.

36:54.450 --> 36:57.270
多谢你的历史课
Thanks for the history lesson.

36:57.280 --> 37:00.150
你要是调查都会知道这些
All it proves is you did the research.

37:00.160 --> 37:02.950
我也做过研究
Same as me.

37:41.300 --> 37:44.070
你结婚了
So you're married?

37:44.270 --> 37:47.740
呃... 不是传统概念的那种
Uh, well...Not in the traditional sense of the word.

37:47.750 --> 37:52.050
斯科菲尔德 我们都是成年人了  把话说明白点
Michael, we're both adults. Put your cards on the table.

37:54.630 --> 37:57.850
好吧 我先说
OK. I'll go first.

37:58.140 --> 38:01.870
呃... 作为这里少数的几名女性之一
As one of the very few women around here,

38:01.880 --> 38:04.460
我习惯用自己的方法对付那些
I'm used to a certain amount...

38:04.470 --> 38:10.120
挑逗和性暗示
of innuendo and flirtation being thrown my way.

38:10.730 --> 38:13.080
我并不喜欢
I'm not used to enjoying it.

38:13.090 --> 38:13.990
听着  莎拉...
Look, Sara...

38:14.000 --> 38:18.790
叫我"唐克雷蒂医生"  让我说完
It's Dr Tancredi. And please let me finish.

38:19.590 --> 38:23.700
我不是个猜忌的女人 但我是个小心谨慎的女人
I'm not ajealous woman. But I'm a careful one.

38:23.710 --> 38:26.860
但不知为什么  在你旁边 我做不到...谨慎
And for some reason,when I'm around you I'm not careful.

38:26.870 --> 38:29.770
-你不需要  -不 我需要
-You don't have to be.  -Yes, I do.

38:29.780 --> 38:33.190
你身上有太多谜了 迈克尔
There's so many questions surrounding you, Michael.

38:33.200 --> 38:36.070
有太多了
 There are way too many.

38:36.080 --> 38:38.720
我们这样  呃..
So here's the deal. Um...

38:38.730 --> 38:42.430
从现在开始 给你打针  只要是有关于医疗的
From now on, your shots, medical concerns,

38:42.440 --> 38:44.670
没有问题  只要是病人-医生的关系
they're all fine, as long as it's doctor-patient.

38:44.680 --> 38:47.760
但如果是那些私人问题 以及各人喜好
But personal questions and favours of any kind

38:47.770 --> 38:51.320
我们以后不要再提起了
are no longer a part of our relationship.

38:52.530 --> 38:56.620
你的那些有关于我的问题...
The questions you have about me...

38:57.360 --> 39:00.620
你会知道答案的
There are answers.

39:08.940 --> 39:10.520
奎因!
Quinn.

39:10.530 --> 39:13.760
我都开始担心了 你们迷路了吗?
Hey, I was getting worried. You guys get lost?

39:13.770 --> 39:15.980
我们想打电话给你来确认精确坐标
We called you again to pinpoint your signal,

39:15.990 --> 39:17.240
可你没接
but you never picked up.

39:17.250 --> 39:19.480
是啊 破手机没电了
Battery went dead on the damn cellphone.

39:19.490 --> 39:20.690
没办法 是不是?

39:20.700 --> 39:23.060
那么 你怎么样?
So, uh... How'd it go?

39:23.070 --> 39:25.440
我一条腿断了
Well, I got a broken leg down here.

39:25.450 --> 39:29.220
听着 我想也许我们把事情都搞砸了
Listen, you know, I think maybe we got off on the wrong foot.

39:29.230 --> 39:31.650
你有上司 我有上司
You got bosses, I got bosses,

39:31.660 --> 39:33.850
到最后 我们还是在一条船上
but at the end of the day we're all on the same team.

39:33.860 --> 39:36.650
对吗? 我们都在收拾残局
Right? Just trying to tie up loose ends.

39:36.660 --> 39:38.310
我再同意你不过了
I could not agree more.

39:38.320 --> 39:43.630
你们能不能找个绳子或是梯子什么的?
Yeah. So can you guys get a rope,or a ladder, or something?

39:46.950 --> 39:49.550
你要干什么?
What the hell's that?

39:49.940 --> 39:51.970
嘿... 嘿!
Hey, hey! Hey!

39:51.980 --> 39:53.570
在收拾残局
Just tying up some loose ends.

39:53.580 --> 39:56.140
你这个婊子养的... 嘿! 嘿!
You son of a... Hey!

39:56.150 --> 40:00.230
嘿 别这么做! 别这么做!
Don't do this. Don't do this!

40:00.410 --> 40:03.830
求你了! 我的腿断了 我站不起来! 你们要帮我!
 Come on, please. My leg is broken. I can't stand.

40:03.840 --> 40:06.630
你不能就这么把他留在这儿 他会死的
You can'tjust leave him down there. He'll die.

40:06.640 --> 40:10.260
他是唯一知道 我们没抓住布伦斯儿子的人
He's the only one who knows we don't have the Burrows kid.

40:10.270 --> 40:13.280
唯一的人
The only one.

40:17.300 --> 40:20.950
你是不是也想下去 丹尼
There's room for you down there too, Danny.

40:22.880 --> 40:24.290
别把我扔在这儿!
Don't leave me like this.

40:24.300 --> 40:26.580
别把我扔下! 求你了!
Don't leave me. Please!

40:26.590 --> 40:28.920
求你了!
Please!

40:33.760 --> 40:35.750
你今天回劳犯团吗?
Coming back to PI today?

40:35.760 --> 40:37.870
在那儿让我有点不爽  知道吗?
It's getting kind of testy in there, you know.

40:37.880 --> 40:40.210
我知道
Yeah.

40:41.630 --> 40:44.360
我要弄清楚一些事
I just needed to find something out.

40:44.370 --> 40:45.920
那是什么?
What the hell's that?

40:45.930 --> 40:47.930
听
Listen.

40:53.290 --> 40:54.790
我是不是应该听见点动静?
Am I supposed to be hearing something?

40:54.800 --> 40:58.860
嘘 耐心听
Shh.Just hold on.

41:13.760 --> 41:16.620
-听见没  -什么?
-There.  -What?

41:16.630 --> 41:18.870
我们等了20分钟就为听这个?
We sat around here for 20 minutes waiting to hear that?

41:18.880 --> 41:21.130
确切的说 是18分钟
18 minutes, actually.

41:21.140 --> 41:23.730
就是这个
And yes.

41:24.170 --> 41:27.050
-那是什么?  -关键
-What was it?  -Keys.

41:27.060 --> 41:28.980
警卫的关键
The guards' keys.

41:28.990 --> 41:31.470
晚上警卫在医务室窗户下面巡逻一次的
18 minutes between each time

41:31.480 --> 41:34.900
时间间隔是18分钟
the guards pass the infirmary windows on their rounds at night.

41:34.910 --> 41:37.150
囚犯在晚上出不去
Cons aren't allowed out after hours.

41:37.160 --> 41:39.130
这是唯一找到时间间隔的方法
Only way I could find out the timing.

41:39.140 --> 41:42.820
-那说明什么?  -说明...
-What does that mean?  -It means...

41:42.830 --> 41:45.520
四天后  在逃亡日那晚
Four days from now, on the night of the escape,

41:45.530 --> 41:48.280
我们有18分钟从医务室下的窗户逃出去
we'll have 18 minutes to get the bars off the window

41:48.290 --> 41:52.250
包括我们七个人穿过电线和翻墙的时间
and for all seven of us to get across the wire and over the wall.

41:52.260 --> 41:55.850
-那能办到吗?  -当然
-Is that doable?  -Of course.

42:08.700 --> 42:10.710
什么事?
What's up?

42:10.720 --> 42:11.990
没事
Nothing.

42:12.000 --> 42:14.810
嘿 我见过这表情 怎么了?
Hey, I know that look. What's up?

42:14.820 --> 42:17.440
挖到了! 挖到了!
I hit it. I hit it!

42:19.200 --> 42:22.110
在那儿 管子! 我们挖到了!
The pipe!

42:22.120 --> 42:24.460
兄弟们 兄弟们
Guys, guys.

42:30.140 --> 42:32.030
说吧 迈克尔 告诉我
Come on, Michael. Talk to me.

42:32.040 --> 42:33.830
你要先听好消息还是坏消息?
You want the good news or the bad news?

42:33.840 --> 42:34.870
好消息
The good.

42:34.880 --> 42:37.860
韦斯特莫兰德和他的钱到了
Westmoreland and his money are in.

42:37.870 --> 42:40.720
-坏消息呢?  -我计算了一下
-What's the bad?  -I've done the math.

42:40.730 --> 42:45.280
我们从医务室窗户翻出去要五分钟
It'll take at least five minutes for us to get the bars off the window in the infirmary,

42:45.290 --> 42:48.750
每个人两分钟翻过电线和墙
two minutes each to get across the wire and over the wall.

42:48.760 --> 42:49.590
所以?
So?

42:49.600 --> 42:52.750
我们只有 18 分钟
We've only got 18 minutes.

42:52.760 --> 42:55.930
我们已经太多人了
We've got too many people.

42:57.630 --> 43:00.840
必须去掉一个
One of 'em has to go.
